      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S featuring the iconic wide-body silhouette and the M96.03 3.6L flat-six powerplant. This example delivers linear power delivery with the characteristic Variocam Plus timing adjustment performing flawlessly. The G96/01 6-speed manual transaxle offers precise gate engagement, paired with a viscous-clutch all-wheel-drive system that maintains excellent mechanical grip. Recent preventative maintenance includes an inspection of the IMS bearing and replacement of the rear main seal. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing the factory-spec subframe and aluminum multi-link rear setup for superb lateral stability. Equipped with four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors, the braking system provides exceptional thermal management and bite. A true driver\u2019s car with a clean underbody and robust compression across all cylinders.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
