    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-cared-for daily driver that balances performance with long-term reliability. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only minor, unavoidable stone chips on the front fascia that are consistent with light highway use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has been kept in a smoke-free environment; the leather bolsters show minimal softening and the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. Every technological feature, including the navigation system, heated seats, and driver-assist sensors, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, benefiting from a documented history of full-synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. We recently completed a 60,000-mile service interval which included a cooling system flush, new spark plugs, and a fresh cabin air filter. The tires are matching top-tier all-seasons with approximately 75% tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced just last season. This is a turn-key car that requires no immediate investment\u2014just a new owner to get behind the wheel.",
